name: AMD Ryzen 9 7950X
description: The AMD Ryzen 9 7950X boasts 16 cores and 32 threads, making it a powerhouse for gaming, streaming, and content creation. With its Zen 4 architecture, it offers significant performance improvements over previous generations.

name: Intel Core i9-12900K
description: Intel's Core i9-12900K features a hybrid architecture with 8 Performance-cores and 8 Efficient-cores, offering a balance of power and efficiency. It's ideal for demanding applications and gaming at the highest settings.

name: AMD Ryzen 7 7700X
description: With 8 cores and 16 threads, the Ryzen 7 7700X is a high-performance CPU that's great for gaming and professional workloads. It offers high speeds and efficiency, thanks to AMD's Zen 4 architecture.

name: Intel Core i7-12700K
description: The Core i7-12700K is a versatile and powerful CPU with 12 cores (8P+4E) and 20 threads, suited for high-end gaming and multitasking. Its performance per dollar makes it an attractive option for gamers and creators alike.
